('John', 'Smith', 'john@mail.com', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824256/avatars/john_u8nwuz.jpg', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824072/covers/john_gdytav.jpg', '$2b$10$.VIO0NQGR/scAtFFVtzHCuIC5Jx9k8c1Fp0pn9vIr8xjuR3oOn2TO', 'I am a visual artist and a graphic designer who focuses on children''s illustrations, book covers, and fun graphics. I am available for book design, illustration, and other commissions. If you are interested in working with me, please send me a message!'), 
('Kenny', 'Yanb', 'kenny@mail.com', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824256/avatars/kenny_b7jr4t.jpg', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824067/covers/kenny_kelqfp.jpg', '$2b$10$.VIO0NQGR/scAtFFVtzHCuIC5Jx9k8c1Fp0pn9vIr8xjuR3oOn2TO', 'By day I am a preschool teacher, but in my spare time I like to paint, do some photography, and make digital artwork. I love beaches, sunsets, and pina coladas. Not currently taking commissions.'), 
