('Maria', 'Kane', 'maria@mail.com', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824256/avatars/maria_rr19tp.jpg', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dckcnn64n/image/upload/v1664824073/covers/maria_xvqk0r.jpg', '$2b$10$.VIO0NQGR/scAtFFVtzHCuIC5Jx9k8c1Fp0pn9vIr8xjuR3oOn2TO', 'I am a psychoanalyst and a literature professor, but in my spare time I love to paint. These are some paintings I have made of people that I love. I do take commissions, but please remember that paintings like these take a lot of time, so if you are shopping for a special occasion or a project with a firm deadline, please let me know as far in advance as possible. Thanks!'),
